'''Tanu Aphidale''' was a member of the [[Judicial Department/Legends|Judicial Department]] prior to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. After [[Director of Personnel|Personnel Director]] [[Lanyss Gutierrace]] was suspended on charges of [[Humanocentrism]], Aphidale was named [[Acting Director]] in her place.

